sequenceDiagram
    participant APP as ClientApp
    participant AUTH as AuthService
    participant CAT as CatalogService
    participant CDN as CDN
    participant EVT as PlayEventStream
    participant ROY as RoyaltyPipeline

    APP->>AUTH: validate session / subscription tier
    AUTH-->>APP: token + tier (free/premium/HiFi)
    APP->>CAT: GET /track/{id}
    CAT-->>APP: manifest {bitrate variants, license, urls}
    Note over APP: pick bitrate from tier + connection
    loop chunked playback
        APP->>CDN: GET audio chunk (selected bitrate)
        CDN-->>APP: chunk bytes
    end
    Note over APP: ≥30s contiguous play threshold reached
    APP-)EVT: play_event {user, track, ts, duration_played}
    EVT-)ROY: stream to royalty aggregator
    ROY->>ROY: dedupe on stream_id, attribute to rights holders
    Note over ROY: monthly aggregation -> payout
